						               													<description>This mission pack is a narrative play expansion for the Warhammer 40,000 Crusade campaign system.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Within this book, you&amp;rsquo;ll find the rules required to play games of Warhammer 40,000 set in the Nachmund Gauntlet, which continues to suffer under the assault of Chaos and xenos forces.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This mission pack has been specifically designed for use in narrative play Crusade games, where your campaigning forces can battle across the war-torn world of Vigilus and beyond. With Marneus Calgar seemingly slain by Abaddon the Despoiler, and the planet&amp;rsquo;s surface overrun by aliens and Heretic Astartes, will your Crusade force emerge as heroes in this time of need or be crushed beneath the boots of their enemies?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This 120-page mission pack includes:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;- Six missions each for Combat Patrol-, Incursion-, Strike Force- and Onslaught-sized games, all set within the beleaguered Nachmund Gauntlet&amp;#10;- Wars of Faith mechanics that allow armies to earn Belief Points to purchase additional abilities&amp;#10;- Priests Battle Traits to be used in Wars of Faith, plus Requisitions and Agendas&amp;#10;- The basic rules for Warhammer 40,000 &amp;ndash; designed to be quickly referenced during your games&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The pack itself is presented in a full Canadian wiro ring-bound book for easy use on the tabletop during games, and it comes with an elastic closure. You will need a copy of the Warhammer 40,000 Core Book to use the contents of this mission pack.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
